NOTICE
======

golars incorporates behavioural specifications derived from the
test suites of several upstream projects, and uses portions of
external UI / CLI designs as layout references. Where noted, Go
test files were written against golars' own API using the
referenced project's tests as a reference for edge cases, null
handling, and corner cases. No code was copied verbatim unless
explicitly called out below.

