sheets - MIT License
Copyright (c) 2024 Maas Lalani
Source: https://github.com/maaslalani/sheets

The TUI browser in `browse/` borrows its grid layout (box-drawing
borders, row-number gutter, column-letter header), modal state model
(NORMAL / VISUAL / COMMAND / FILTER), and vim-style keybinding
conventions from sheets. Implementation is original; no code is
copied. Lookups for cells are wired through golars' Arrow buffers
instead of an in-memory dense matrix.

