Apache Arrow / arrow-go - Apache 2.0 License
Source: https://github.com/apache/arrow-go

arrow-go is the only runtime dependency in the core packages. Every
Series is an arrow.Array; every chunked operation routes through
arrow.Chunked. golars does not wrap or reimplement arrow types.

